           private class WsdlProcessingResult { 




               private Collection<WsdlParser.ServiceInfo> parsedServices = new ArrayList<>(); 




               private List<WarningDeviation> warnings = new ArrayList<>(); 




           } 






https://confluence.niis.org/display/XRDDEV/API+backend+implementation#APIbackendimplementation-Layering
https://softwareengineering.stackexchange.com/questions/198783/why-is-it-a-good-idea-for-lower-application-layers-not-to-be-aware-of-higher

